            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1269773931,
            "creation_date": 1269773931,
            "body": "<p>No one stops you from sending binary and text data instead of HTML-pages using http protocol. That is whats servlets are for. So I would use the tomcat server. <\/p>\n",
